project/
├── docker-compose.yml        # Haupt Compose File 
├── .env                      # Secrets / ENV (nicht committen)
├── .env.example              # Dummy ENV 
├── .nginx/
│   └── default.conf          # NGINX config 
├── wordpress/                # WP Files (Docker volume gemountet)
└── db_data/                  # DB Daten (Docker volume)


3️⃣ Start Befehle

Dev:

docker compose -f docker-compose-dev.yaml up


Prod:

docker compose -f docker-compose-prod.yaml up -d
